# Active Work Directory

This directory contains active work being tracked by the spec-workflow system.

Each active feature has its own subdirectory with:
- `tasks.md` - Link to the actual tasks document in `specs/<feature>/tasks.md`
- `status.md` - Current status snapshot

## Structure

```
active/
├── current-feature-link -> ../specs/current-feature/tasks.md
└── status.md - Global status of active work
```
